<h1>诗</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shī</span><span class=alesi>(shi1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 诗 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 诗</h2><div class=abo>
